{"title":"Panorama Cycles Taiga EXP Is a Drop or Flat-Bar 29er Tourer","link":"https://theradavist.com/panorama-cycles-taiga-exp","date":1773394777000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Panorama-Taiga-EXP-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Panorama-Taiga-EXP-1.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Panorama-Taiga-EXP-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Panorama-Taiga-EXP-1.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><em><a href=\"https://theradavist.com/tag/panorama-cycles\" target=\"_blank\">Panorama Cycles</a> just announced the third generation of its Taiga touring bike with some major tweaks. The Taiga EXP is designed for <a href=\"https://www.panoramacycles.com/products/taiga-exp\" target=\"_blank\">drop</a> or <a href=\"https://www.panoramacycles.com/products/taiga-exp-fb\" target=\"_blank\">flat bars</a>…</em><span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Panorama-Taiga-EXP-2.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Panorama-Taiga-EXP-2.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Panorama-Taiga-EXP-2.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Panorama-Taiga-EXP-2.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Panorama-Taiga-EXP-15.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Panorama-Taiga-EXP-15.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Panorama-Taiga-EXP-15.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Panorama-Taiga-EXP-15.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3>Taiga EXP Updates Quick Hits</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Addition of a frame size (M/L)</li>\n<li>Updated geometry (slightly more aggressive angles and corrected for 120mm suspension).</li>\n<li>A new steel fork option has been added to the existing carbon fork.</li>\n<li>Now available in a flat handlebar configuration</li>\n<li>Internal cable routing for rear dynamo light.</li>\n<li>New rear wheel dropouts design</li>\n<li>New CNC-machined chainstay yoke</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Panorama-Taiga-EXP-3.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Panorama-Taiga-EXP-3.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Panorama-Taiga-EXP-3.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Panorama-Taiga-EXP-3.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Panorama-Taiga-EXP-6.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Panorama-Taiga-EXP-6.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Panorama-Taiga-EXP-6.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Panorama-Taiga-EXP-6.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Panorama-Taiga-EXP-4.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Panorama-Taiga-EXP-4.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Panorama-Taiga-EXP-4.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Panorama-Taiga-EXP-4.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>Carrying forward the DNA of the Taïga EXP, this third generation is designed for riders who want to cover long distances across all types of terrain. Its versatile geometry promotes a comfortable and efficient riding position, whether for bikepacking, off-road ultra races, or all-terrain rides.</p>\n<p>Built from Reynolds 725 steel, the frame uses butted tubing to reduce weight while maximizing strength. Each frame size receives a size-specific tube selection, ensuring optimal performance while preserving the lively ride quality and comfort that steel is known for.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Panorama-Taiga-EXP-151.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Panorama-Taiga-EXP-151.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Panorama-Taiga-EXP-151.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Panorama-Taiga-EXP-151.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Panorama-Taiga-EXP-154.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Panorama-Taiga-EXP-154.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Panorama-Taiga-EXP-154.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/Panorama-Taiga-EXP-154.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>The Taïga EXP Gen3 is now offered with a steel or carbon fork, each designed with geometry adjusted to remain compatible with a 120 mm suspension setup.</p>\n<p>A durable and extremely versatile adventure bike, the Taïga EXP Gen3 is a true off-road travel platform, designed to go far and last long.</p>\n<p>Check out more of the <em> <a href=\"https://www.panoramacycles.com/products/taiga-exp\" target=\"_blank\">drop</a> or <a href=\"https://www.panoramacycles.com/products/taiga-exp-fb\" target=\"_blank\">flat bar</a> Taiga EXP </em>at <a href=\"https://www.panoramacycles.com/products/taiga-exp-fb\" target=\"_blank\">Panorama Cycles</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/panorama-cycles-taiga-exp\">Panorama Cycles Taiga EXP Is a Drop or Flat-Bar 29er Tourer</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://cms.theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"9d99cb63bce483f4b4c88d66e4496e2b907fe73098bc78e219fe8d345bf58c14","category":"Cycling"}